      "widgets_values": [
        "## BD Background Removal\\n\\n**SAM3 + pymatting** subject cutout with alpha matting, decontamination, and edge keying.\\n\\n- **rgba** - transparent cutout\\n- **rgb_white_bg / rgb_black_bg** - flattened composites\\n- **sticker** - white outline (set `sticker_outline` > 0)\\n- **mask** -> BD Mask Batch Index -> MaskToImage to inspect\\n\\nTips: enable **key_gaps** to clear open background gaps between limbs; **decontaminate** removes color halos; raise **matting_erode/dilate** for cleaner edges."
      ],
      "title": "\u2139\ufe0f About \u2014 \ud83e\udde0 BrainDead Background Removal"
